{{infobox water buffalo breed | name = Krabue buffalo | image = BUFFALO159.JPG | country = [[Thailand]] | status = not at risk | use = plowing, meat, milk | coat = black, brown, grey, albino | type = swamp}}
The '''Krabue buffalo''' ({{lang|th|กระบือ}} (''krabue'') being the [[Thai language|Thai]] word for "water buffalo") also known as the '''Siamese buffalo''', '''Thai water buffalo''' or '''Thai swamp buffalo''' is a large [[breed]] of [[water buffalo]] indigenous to [[Thailand]].<ref name=Cockrill/>
